rows.label: qst106005_msg0001
rows.name:
Welcome to Bluesky Nopon
University, mo. Are you the
ones for the trial enrollment, mo?

rows.label: qst106005_msg0002
rows.name:
Yes, mo. I've come to acquire
the refinement of a lady, mo.

rows.label: qst106005_msg0004
rows.name:
I don't know what you're
talking about, but let's
start the class anyway, mo.

rows.label: qst106005_msg0005
rows.name:
If you can keep up with the
classes until the end, you will
acquire a fine education, mo.

rows.label: qst106005_msg0006
rows.name: Please do your best to keep up, mo.

rows.label: qst106005_msg0008
rows.name:
Well then, let's begin the first
period class right away, mo.

rows.label: qst106005_msg0009
rows.name: The first period is Forestry, mo.

rows.label: qst106005_msg0010
rows.name:
Now, Hana-san, please read the sentence
written on the blackboard, mo.
